  "text": "While all of the existing SWFS possess great features and address many aspects of workflow specification, execution and management problems, it is unrealistic to expect one system to cover all the bases. The Workflow Bus project [CITATION_1] instead tries to leverage multiple existing workflow systems to compliment each other in implementing aggregated functions and services.",
